<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Sat, 22 Jan 2022 09:49:41 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>5G 疑影響飛行安全，美國航空公司警告倡延遲推出 5G 服務</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/22/airlines-ask-biden-administration-for-immediate-intervention-on-5g/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=airlines-ask-biden-administration-for-immediate-intervention-on-5g</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jan 2022 09:48:44 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[5G]]></category><category><![CDATA[美國]]></category><category><![CDATA[航空安全]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1081724</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>美國兩間電訊公司 AT&#38;T 和 Verizon 將在週三正式啟用 5G 網絡，有當地多間航空公司向美國 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">美國兩間電訊公司 AT&amp;T 和 Verizon 將在週三正式啟用 5G 網絡，有當地多間航空公司向美國政府、聯邦航空管理局（FAA）和聯邦通信委員會（FCC）發聯署信，稱 5G 網絡將為航空安全帶來危機，航空公司或被迫取消大量航班，要求政府立即介入。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1081725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/D89904DB-CC3C-442E-8900-6DA255EA9B84-694x379.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="379" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/D89904DB-CC3C-442E-8900-6DA255EA9B84-694x379.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/D89904DB-CC3C-442E-8900-6DA255EA9B84-1280x700.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/D89904DB-CC3C-442E-8900-6DA255EA9B84-768x420.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/D89904DB-CC3C-442E-8900-6DA255EA9B84-1536x840.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/D89904DB-CC3C-442E-8900-6DA255EA9B84-2048x1119.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/D89904DB-CC3C-442E-8900-6DA255EA9B84.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">早前美國交通部及聯邦航空管理局關注訊號會干擾飛機，要求美國兩大電訊商 AT&amp;T 和 Verizon 推遲啟用新的 C 頻譜 5G（C-Band 5G）網絡服務，至本月 19 日才推出啟用。但日前美國航空、達美航空、聯合航空和聯邦快遞等十間公司的行政總裁聯署去信白宮國家經濟委員會、運輸部、聯邦航空局及聯邦通訊委員會，表示新的 C 頻譜 5G 服務可能導致大量飛機停飛，例如波音 777、空巴 A340 等廣體客機。信中提及「如果 AT&amp;T 和 Verizon 本周開始啟用其新的 C 頻譜 5G 網絡，或將出現災難性混亂。」航空公司憂慮，5G 信號塔或對飛機高度儀等敏感儀器的運作造成干擾，這對飛機進行低視野方式著陸（low-visibility landings）至關重要，希望 AT&amp;T 和 Verizon 不要在機場 2 英里（約 3.2 公里）範圍內啟動 5G 信號塔，以避免出現干擾。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1081726" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/34843F9A-D2D0-4B56-BA1C-786AFBFE85E8-694x380.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="380" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/34843F9A-D2D0-4B56-BA1C-786AFBFE85E8-694x380.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/34843F9A-D2D0-4B56-BA1C-786AFBFE85E8-1280x701.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/34843F9A-D2D0-4B56-BA1C-786AFBFE85E8-768x420.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/34843F9A-D2D0-4B56-BA1C-786AFBFE85E8-1536x841.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/34843F9A-D2D0-4B56-BA1C-786AFBFE85E8-2048x1121.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/34843F9A-D2D0-4B56-BA1C-786AFBFE85E8.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1081727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2A21E7EA-AA7F-46B4-8ED6-5433E7856BAF-694x373.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2A21E7EA-AA7F-46B4-8ED6-5433E7856BAF-694x373.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2A21E7EA-AA7F-46B4-8ED6-5433E7856BAF-1280x689.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2A21E7EA-AA7F-46B4-8ED6-5433E7856BAF-768x413.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2A21E7EA-AA7F-46B4-8ED6-5433E7856BAF-1536x827.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2A21E7EA-AA7F-46B4-8ED6-5433E7856BAF-2048x1102.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2A21E7EA-AA7F-46B4-8ED6-5433E7856BAF.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">信中又提及，航班取消將令數以萬計美國人被迫滯留海外，並造成航班混亂，因而要求白宮和相關機構立即介入事件，避免對航空旅客、托運人士、供應鏈和所需醫療用品造成業務中斷。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2022/01/17/tech/faa-5g-flight-restrictions/index.html">CNN</a>、<a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-faa-oks-45-commercial-airplane-fleet-operations-after-5g-deployment-2022-01-16/">reuters</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
