</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>中國無針注射機械人「后羿」 過程可在半秒內完成減低痛楚</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/22/china-launches-needle-free-robot-houyi-that-can-reduce-pain-in-half-a-second/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=china-launches-needle-free-robot-houyi-that-can-reduce-pain-in-half-a-second</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jan 2022 09:48:11 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[中國]]></category><category><![CDATA[后羿]]></category><category><![CDATA[無針頭疫苗注射機械人]]></category><category><![CDATA[疫苗]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1081719</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>新冠肺炎病毒傳播至今，相信未來仍有不少人需要接種疫苗。日前有中國團隊發表一款全自動無針頭疫苗注射機械人名為「后 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">新冠肺炎病毒傳播至今，相信未來仍有不少人需要接種疫苗。日前有中國團隊發表一款全自動無針頭疫苗注射機械人名為「后羿」，志在減輕醫務人員負擔。據資料顯示，「后羿」可利用人體 3D 模型識別算法及自適應機器人技術，準確識別疫苗注射部位及角度，並透過高壓水柱射流，完成無針注射，減少痛感。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1081720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0B6F6251-58AD-4431-9B5A-C7661AF37B61.jpeg" alt="" width="608" height="434" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1081721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1CF25590-99FA-4801-BE48-F733C6570E0B.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="338" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1081722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/88AF6FCC-D3CC-42A4-9010-4815C69F98E1.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="338" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據中國媒體報導，上海同濟大學副教授齊鵬團隊日前發佈中國首款「自主智能無針疫苗注射機械人」。該機械人由團隊及非夕科技、北京快舒爾醫療技術、中國心血管醫生創新俱樂部（CCI）共同開發完成。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">「后羿」可快速自動擬合人體對應部位的 3D 模型，識別疫苗注射部位及注射角度；同時採用七軸力控自適應機械臂應用高精度力控貼合算法，能確保注射器末端垂直緊貼注射部位，提升注射效果，減低痛楚。透過高壓水柱，機械人可推動藥劑經過極細的噴嘴，形成高壓射流穿過皮膚，直接進入到注射部位，達到無針注射。整個注射過程可在半秒內完成，且注射精度可精確到 0.01 毫升，適用於不同疫苗的劑量要求。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_81381"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/exP3uyfeVRE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="http://vblog.people.com.cn/index/playvideo/contentid/498112">人民網</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
