</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>iPhone SE 3 最新渲染圖曝光，傳加入 M 字額設計＋取消 Touch ID</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/22/iphone-se-3-touch-id/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=iphone-se-3-touch-id</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jan 2022 09:45:29 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone SE 3]]></category><category><![CDATA[touch id]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1081558</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>知名 Apple 爆料人 David Kowalski 及外國媒體 TenTechReview 共同發布 iP [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>知名 Apple 爆料人 David Kowalski 及外國媒體 TenTechReview 共同發布 iPhone SE 3 的最新 CAD 渲染圖及尺寸，顯示將加入 M 字額瀏海螢幕設計及取消 Touch ID 主畫面按鈕，預計於 3 月至 4 月推出。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Here&#39;s a promised 4K all-around video &#8211; <a href="https://t.co/svN1OD20r3">https://t.co/svN1OD20r3</a> <a href="https://t.co/OlqVpti9Pv">pic.twitter.com/OlqVpti9Pv</a></p><p>&mdash; xleaks7 (David Kowalski) (@xleaks7) <a href="https://twitter.com/xleaks7/status/1482078692163653636?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 14, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>相片中的 SE 3 與 SE 2 有別，改用「瀏海」螢幕設計外，亦取消 Touch ID 主畫面按鈕，外型恍如 2018 年推出的 iPhone XR。從 SE 3 的機背可見，SE 3 依舊沿用單鏡頭及閃光燈設計，Apple 標誌亦同樣印於機背中央位置。唯一與 XR 不同的是，SE 3 的後置補光燈及咪高風將轉移至主鏡頭右方。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_6E22ED595904-1.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_6E22ED595904-1-567x580.jpeg" alt="" width="567" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_6E22ED595904-1-567x580.jpeg 567w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_6E22ED595904-1-880x900.jpeg 880w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_6E22ED595904-1-768x785.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_6E22ED595904-1.jpeg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 567px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-17-下午 5.22.07.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-17-下午 5.22.07-694x447.png" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-17-下午 5.22.07-694x447.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-17-下午 5.22.07-1280x825.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-17-下午 5.22.07-768x495.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-17-下午 5.22.07-1536x990.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-17-下午 5.22.07.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>他們預計 SE 3 的尺寸與 SE 2 一樣，皆為 138.4 x 67.3 x 7.3 毫米，鏡頭凸起 8.2 毫米，預計螢幕尺寸約 5.69 寸。而電源按鈕及 SIM 卡槽將設於機身右側，音量按鈕及靜音開關則設於機身左側，底部將放置 Lightning 介面及揚聲器。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_85057"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LVdetghOxS8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://tentechreview.com">TenTechReview</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
